        [
          {
            "text": "Chirping sound when compressor is off or on"
          },
          {
            "text": "Magnet Clutch contact noise"
          },
          {
            "text": "Adjustment of clearance between center piece and rotor Check for rattling of rotor bearings and compressor boss, if necessary. Clutch Set , , Replace the compressor",
